<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="images/cheese-burger.png">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:ital,wght@0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,300;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.1.1/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-KfkfwYDsLkIlwQp6LFnl8zNdLGxu9YAA1QvwINks4PhcElQSvqcyVLLD9aMhXd13uQjoXtEKNosOWaZqXgel0g==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <title>Kashyap's Food Junction </title>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar target">
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">
            <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
            <span>Home</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">
            <i class="fas fa-utensils"></i>
            <span>Meals</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">
            <i class="fas fa-pizza-slice"></i>
            <span>Pizza</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">
            <i class="fas fa-hamburger"></i>
            <span>Burger</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-link">
            <i class="fas fa-blender-phone"></i>
            <span>Contact</span>
        </a>
    </nav>
    <div class="menu target"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- first section -->

        <section class="section-1">
            <h1 class="section-heading">
                Kashyap's Food Junction 
            </h1>
            <div class="section-1-icons">
                <i class="fas fa-chocolate change"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-stroopwafel"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-cheese"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-drumstick-bite"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-hot coffee"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-apple-alt"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-ice-cream"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-pizza"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-burgur"></i>
                <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- second section -->
        <section class="section-2">
            <h2 class="section-heading">
                Meals We Love
            </h2>
            <div class="cards-container">
                <div class="card">
                    <img class="card-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Noodles">
                    <h3 class="card-name">Noodles</h3>
                    <button class="card-btn">Order Now</button>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <img class="card-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="">
                    <h3 class="card-name">Pizza</h3>
                    <button class="card-btn">Order Now</button>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <img class="card-img" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQOeQ1V9ewZMSu9IYKaBY-B6FDg8djaWz_fIA&usqp=CAU" alt="">
                    <h3 class="card-name">Dosa</h3>
                    <button class="card-btn">Order Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- third section -->
        <section class="section-3">
            <h2 class="section-heading">
                Our Food Gallery
            </h2>
            <div class="gallery">
                <a class="gallery-link" title="Order Now">
                    <img class="food-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
                    <h3 class="food-name">Hamburger</h3>
                    <p class="food-description">
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Eaque error, velit itaque distinctio numquam nobis.
                    </p>
                </a>
                <a class="gallery-link" title="Order Now">
                    <img class="food-img" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQ-dZZl0-leKxdZHdZerg7HORq9b8KeYugvqw&usqp=CAU">
                    <h3 class="food-name">Salmon</h3>
                    <p class="food-description">
                      Testy selmon 
                      Based on great preservative 
                      
                    </p>
                </a>
                <a class="gallery-link" title="Order Now">
                    <img class="food-img" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcS-_DuIfFBH_iahf0sV2P1Lura6LegDaDBOlw&usqp=CAU">
                    <h3 class="food-name">Pancakes</h3>
                    <p class="food-description">
                        High protiens 
                      non vegetrains 
                      
                    </p>
                </a>
                <a class="gallery-link" title="Order Now">
                    <img class="food-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
                    <h3 class="food-name">Burgur</h3>
                    <p class="food-description">
                        Latest hamburger 
                      Based on germany preparation 
                      
                    </p>
                </a>
                <a class="gallery-link" title="Order Now">
                    <img class="food-img" src="data:image/jpeg;base64,>
                    <h3 class="food-name">Idli sambhar </h3>
                    <p class="food-description">
                       South Indian 
                      Testy 
                      Contains full energy
                      
                    </p>
                </a>
                <a class="gallery-link" title="Order Now">
                    <img class="food-img" src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTCR43w3Q7OUfFebiM3opULFyFwi7Q8cmt1Ng&usqp=CAU">
                    <h3 class="food-name">Veggies</h3>
                    <p class="food-description">
                      Spinach. Share on Pinterest Andersen Ross/Getty Images. ...
 Kale is a very popular leafy green vegetable with several health benefits. ...
Broccoli. ...
Peas. ...
Sweet potatoes. ...
Beets. ...
Carrots. ...
Fermented vegetables.
                    </p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- fourth section -->
        <section class="section-4">
            <div class="section-4-text">
                <h2 class="section-4-heading">Get me started</h2>
                <p class="section-4-p">Get information on available food</p>
            </div>
            <form class="sign-up">
                <input type="email" class="signup-form-input" placeholder="Enter Your Email">
                <button type="submit" class="signup-form-btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
                </button>
            </form>
            <p class="copyright">
                Priya kashyap &copy; 2023
            </p>
        </section>

    </div>
    
    <script src="index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
